title: J-Law gives piggyback to pal Aziz Ansari
text: J-Law gives piggyback to pal Aziz Ansari Tuesday, 13 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 12(ANI): Jennifer Lawrence seems to be getting close with her new pal Aziz Ansari.* Washington D.C., Oct. 12(ANI): Jennifer Lawrence seems to be getting close with her new pal Aziz Ansari. The 25-year-old actress gave piggyback ride to the 32-year-old actor on their way out of an SNL after party in the New York City , reports TMZ.com. According to sources, the shindig was hosted by Amy Schumer, who is also writing a screenplay with 'The Huger Games' star. (ANI)
